<wp_sync_description><p>OcpSoft is considering a new development environment for our projects, and we need your help. Our current development environment is annoying, painful at times. So the question is: "What development environment would you recommend?"</p>
</wp_sync_description>

<wp_sync_link>http://ocpsoft.org/opensource/java-web-app-development-whats-your-secret/</wp_sync_link>

